162
00:08:30,833 --> 00:08:32,375
My grandfather's friends are
having a party tomorrow night

163
00:08:32,458 --> 00:08:34,625
and they're... picky
eaters, so I was hoping

164
00:08:34,708 --> 00:08:37,708
I could borrow your
culinary expertise.

165
00:08:37,791 --> 00:08:39,583
